   <titleInfo>
      <title>2Mg64 Robertson Site, Morgan County, Alabama. Burial #3, partly flexed adult burial overlying Burial #4, extended burial. Burial #5, consisting of only a femur fragment, lies at left. By the skull of Burial #4 lies a steatite pipe (F.S.#2). A greenstone celt (F.S.#3) and a greenstone celt fragment (F.S.#4) lie near the left shoulder of Burial #4</title>
